1873	  // For vendors, archive is PER-VENDOR — flip their own RFQVendor row, never the
1874	  // global RFQItem.rfqItem_archive flag (which would hide the item from Sourcing and
1875	  // other factories). 'archive' url means the click came from the archive view → restore.
